us.pserver.revok.container

Class ObjectContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • us.pserver.revok.container.ObjectContainer

  • public class ObjectContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Objects container on server, biding them to a recovery String key. ObjectContainer is secure for multithreaded environments.
    Version:
    1.1 - 201506
    Author:
    Juno Roesler - juno@pserver.com
